      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 46,
      "message": "Suggestion - it is best to completely avoid setting and then removing IP values in favor of just ignoring what is unwanted. Since the ImmutableConsumerDmaapModel fields are required and not setting a fields results in IllegalStateException, I'd recommend adding @Nullable to ConsumerDmaapModel IP fields. This will make them optional and all ip set/remove lines can be removed.",
